GDT is seeking to hire a Big Data Engineer to help with our current demands in big data technologies. We are looking for strong, experienced candidates with 3-4 years of big data ecosystem experience who have done similar work elsewhere (Financial Services experience is a plus) * Strong experience in Hadoop platform and data architecture * Strong experience in use of open source tools such as: Hadoop, Hive, HBase, Spark, Storm, Kafka and file storage formats (Parquet, Avro, ORC) * Candidate must have prior experience working with one or more of the following: Cloudera Hadoop Distribution, Hortonworks Data Platform, MapR, Microsoft HDInsights * Fluency in several programming languages such as Java, Scala or Python with the ability to pick up new languages and technologies quickly
